    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and optimized by the high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing system. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with mechanical precision, paired with a variable M-differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from recent trailing arm bushing refreshes and a documented subframe reinforcement. While showing honest patina consistent with its driver-focused history, the compression remains within spec across all cylinders and the valvetrain is exceptionally quiet. A true driver\u2019s example with the critical rod bearing service already addressed.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
